{"title":"Esker Updates Its Hardtail Lineup for 2025","link":"https://theradavist.com/esker-update-hardtail-lineup-for-2025/","date":1741611643000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/EskerCycles2025Updates.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/EskerCycles2025Updates.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/EskerCycles2025Updates.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/EskerCycles2025Updates.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/esker-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Cycles</a> has refreshed most of their hardtail lineup for 2025. Let’s check the models and their updates out below…</em><span></span></p>\n<p>These updates include the brand’s two classic hardtail models, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/locke-and-his-esker-cycles-hayduke-singlespeed-29er/\" target=\"_blank\">Hayduke</a> and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-japhy-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Japhy</a>, both of which got geo tweaks, including more stack height. The two newest members of the Esker family, Lorax Ti and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-hayduke-lvs-longtail-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Hayduke LVS</a>, get some minor tweaks. The Lorax, Smokey, and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-smokey-ti-review-hardcore-hardtail/\" target=\"_blank\">Smokey Ti</a> have remained the same for 2025.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/hayduke\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Esker Hayduke Hardtail</a> Updates Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Simplified sizing range: SM, MD, LG, XL</li>\n<li>Steel Frames: $1000</li>\n<li>Steel Completes: Starting at $3000</li>\n<li>Ti Frames: $2500</li>\n<li>Ti Completes: Starting at $4500</li>\n<li>Top Tube Bolts: Increased snack carrying capacity</li>\n<li>Updated Geo: Longer wheelbase, Lower center of gravity (increased BB Drop), taller stack</li>\n<li>Increased Tire Clearance: Clearance for up to a 29×3.0 tire (clearance may vary by drivetrain choice, rim width, dropout position and actual tire measurement)</li>\n<li>Improved Chainstay Heel Clearance: Not a ton, but Esker tried to scooch things in a bit for those exploring the backcountry in their favorite hiking boots.</li>\n<li>Mid-Mount Rack Mounts: Rack mounts in the middle of the seatstay</li>\n<li>‘Hitching Post’: Seat Tube bottle boss/gear strap – Allows for increased seatpost insertion *Titanium Frames Only*</li>\n<li>Optimized Dropper Port Location: Port has been moved up the seattube to ease cable routing.</li>\n<li>Custom Chainstay Protector: Its protection for your chainstay…and its custom</li>\n<li>New Logo and Finish: *Titanium Frames Only*</li>\n<li>New Paint Colors: *Steel Frames Only*</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Hayduke Details</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_01.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_01.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Hayduke Colors</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_01.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_01.png?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_01.png?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_frame_details_01.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_titanium.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_titanium.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_titanium.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_titanium.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Geo and 2025 <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/hayduke-ti\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Hayduke Ti</a></em></p>\n<h3>Hayduke Geometry</h3>\n<p>The Hayduke becomes even more touring-oriented with an increase in tire clearance, geo tweaks, mid-mount rack mounts, and a new “Hitching Post” seat tube bottle boss gear strap. These changes not only help the Hayduke become a better bike for backcountry adventures, multi-day tours, and bikepacking races alike, but they also help differentiate it from the Japhy more effectively.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_LVS.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_LVS.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_LVS.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hayduke_LVS.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/hayduke-lvs\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Esker Hayduke LVS</a> Mid-Length Hardtail Updates Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frames  Starting $2950 MSRP</li>\n<li>Ti Completes:  Starting at $4950 MSRP</li>\n<li>Top Tube Bolts:  Increased snack carrying capacity!</li>\n<li>Updated Geo:  Increased stack offset with a longer Effective TT</li>\n<li>Mid-Mount Rack Mounts:  Rack mounts in the middle of the Seatstay</li>\n<li>‘Hitching Post’: Seat Tube bottle boss/gear strap – Allows for increased seatpost insertion.</li>\n<li>Custom Chainstay Protector:  Its protection for your chainstay…and its custom</li>\n<li>New Logo and Finish: <em>*Titanium Frames Only*</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For 2025, the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-radavist-product-awards-and-top-10-articles-of-2023/\" target=\"_blank\">award-winning Hayduke LVS</a> remains unchanged but with a few key updates outlined above. This is the most legit production touring bike on the market for rough terrain where a suspension fork is necessary.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/japhy\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Esker Japhy</a> Hardtail Updates Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Simplified sizing range: SM, MD, LG, XL</li>\n<li>Updated Geo: Increased Stack offset with a longer Effective TT</li>\n<li>Removed Seatstay Bridge: Increased compliance and ride quality</li>\n<li>New Chainstay Yoke: Slimmer profile *Titanium Frames Only*</li>\n<li>‘Hitching Post’: Seat Tube bottle boss/gear strap – Allows for increased seatpost insertion *Titanium Frames Only*</li>\n<li>Optimized Dropper Port Location: Port has been moved up the seattube to ease cable routing.</li>\n<li>Bolt-On Cable Routing: Allowing for bolt-on frame bags and stealthier routing for those using wireless shifting or no shifting at all</li>\n<li>Custom Chainstay Protector: It’s protection for your chainstay…and its custom</li>\n<li>New Logo Finish: *Titanium Frames Only*</li>\n<li>New Paint Colors: *Steel Frames Only*</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_01.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_02.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_03.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_04.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_details_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Japhy Details</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_01.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_01.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_frame_colors_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Japhy Colors</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_geometry.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_geometry.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_geometry.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_geometry.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_titanium.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_titanium.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_titanium.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_japhy_titanium.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Geo and <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/japhy-ti\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Japhy Ti</a></em></p>\n<h3>Japhy Geometry</h3>\n<p>The Japhy remains in the lineup as the lighter, quicker, and more agile short-travel hardtail. Use it for XC riding, big backcountry day missions, or just everyday riding. It lacks touring accutremonts but got an increase in stack height across all sizes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hitching_post_detail.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hitching_post_detail.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hitching_post_detail.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/2025_esker_hitching_post_detail.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Esker Cycles Hitching Post for Titanium Frames</h3>\n<p>All updated Esker Cycles titanium frames see the addition of the “Hitching Post”. A modification to the seat tube that brings the water bottle mounts further forward. Allowing for greater seatpost insertion while also providing a place to strap down additional gear.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/Locke-and-His-Esker-Hayduke-SS29er-32.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/Locke-and-His-Esker-Hayduke-SS29er-32.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/Locke-and-His-Esker-Hayduke-SS29er-32.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/Locke-and-His-Esker-Hayduke-SS29er-32.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Esker-Hayduke-LVS-Review-38.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Esker-Hayduke-LVS-Review-38.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Esker-Hayduke-LVS-Review-38.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Esker-Hayduke-LVS-Review-38.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/The-Esker-Japhy-is-one-Scrappy-29er-61.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/The-Esker-Japhy-is-one-Scrappy-29er-61.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/The-Esker-Japhy-is-one-Scrappy-29er-61.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/The-Esker-Japhy-is-one-Scrappy-29er-61.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>If you’re curious about these Esker models, check out our extended library of reviews from each of these models in our Related archives below!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-update-hardtail-lineup-for-2025/\">Esker Updates Its Hardtail Lineup for 2025</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"cd59dac123f84993f2fb087036646e0c8c05cfd6e958dbcae96e9c4a3f31f304","category":"Cycling"}